data.description: Make this your new home located in the desirable community of Stonebridge in Waldorf MD. The open floor plan is ideal for entertaining and everyday living. Lay in the warmth of the morning sun on the oversized deck that runs the full length of the home.  Additional features include: 3 bedrooms, 3 full and 1 half bathroom, kitchen with island, stainless steel appliances and a lower level living room/den/office.  ***FRESH NEW PAINT JOB*** and ***BRAND NEW CARPET***in recreation  room which makes this home even more desirable! This home is positioned in the heart of Charles County; close to schools, shopping, restaurants, hospitals, Route 301 and Route 5, and within a 20-mile radius of 9 military bases. Also, just minutes away from a commuter Park and Ride  lot for your convenience  if you  work in DC or VA areas!  You will never feel too far away from everything you need!
